Type: Package
Package: varutils
Title: Utility Functions for VAR Analisys
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ricardo Semião e Castro
Maintainer: Ricardo Semião e Castro <ricardo.semiao@outlook.com>
Description: Functions for commonly needed ggplot graphs for Vector
    Auto-Regressive models, like IRF's, FEVD's, predict graphs, and VAR
    residual analysis. Soon to contain functions for common tests and
    statistics, and other VAR-like objects.
